{"tid":896084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"激嬲左女朋友","createTime":"2018-11-09T16:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T10:03:54.000Z","uid":213538,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e7412daa85895c3191dcc759f55804935f5e6f6e","tid":896084,"uid":213538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:49:11.000Z","msg":"今日佢生日<br />\n我係佢第一個陪佢過生日既男朋友<br />\n佢都係我第一個女朋友同埋我第一次同女朋友過生日<br />\n身為男朋友既我今日陪佢食晚飯<br />\n咁佢呢幾日都不斷食左幾個生日蛋糕<br />\n我諗住佢會食厭所以冇買比佢<br />\n佢覺得我冇將佢放係心入面<br />\n巴絲們覺得我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c36090739877614f173d2595266ead833844a4","tid":896084,"uid":127120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:51:04.000Z","msg":"男人之家都幾小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f965643f903015e515105aa87a0ffc15669703e2","tid":896084,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"無興趣知啲小學雞拍拖點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac8bb8a2b2ea990f3d0667fdb7b5526ed219a52","tid":896084,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:51:54.000Z","msg":"咁基本既野都冇 抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9353f32f0a473d2df1755fd8a241b053fb882d4f","tid":896084,"uid":10536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:53:11.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快手買番禮物同生日🎂加張生日道歉卡賠罪啦"},{"pid":"7d73b28113c39a6b6a1ae04ce7a2417599c584ff","tid":896084,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"做返個套哄返佢啦"},{"pid":"a1026438bacbf581f9e7b62286c3341f25e5d776","tid":896084,"uid":206388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"咁少事都嬲 飛左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces